lead_paragraph: Cypriot tennis player Marcos Baghdatis has withdrawn from next month's Rio Olympics after failing to recover from an elbow injury, the world number 42 said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Baghdatis Withdraws From Rio Due to Injury
